thread.title: Mexico central bank sells $200 mln in currency auction
thread.title_full: Mexico central bank sells $200 mln in currency auction | Reuters

author: Reuters
title: Mexico central bank sells $200 mln in currency auction
text: MEXICO CITY Aug 13 The central bank of Mexico sold $200 million on Thursday at an average price of 16.3504 pesos per dollar, the bank said, part of an auction program to boost foreign exchange liquidity following a slump in the peso. (Reporting by Joanna Zuckerman Bernstein)
